<i>Legend of Fei</i>

16
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:07,940
<i>Episode 16</i>

17
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,160
Remember,

18
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,230
Water Cutting of the North Blade

19
00:02:42,230 --> 00:02:44,160
is complicated and changeable.

20
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:46,800
But it has its own rules.

21
00:03:17,190 --> 00:03:19,520
It’s OK. I’ll stall them first.

22
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,550
You underestimate them.

23
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:25,390
People from Dragon Sect

24
00:03:25,390 --> 00:03:27,550
all have good ears.

25
00:03:27,550 --> 00:03:28,720
It’s no different from speaking

26
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:31,360
in front of them when you
talk so quietly.

27
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,720
I can hear everything you say.

28
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,440
You’re still alive?

29
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,450
We will give you to our master

30
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,000
to see how he will punish you.

31
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:43,270
Let’s deal with the two of them first.

32
00:03:43,670 --> 00:03:44,630
Wait.

33
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,080
Have you considered it?

34
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,160
Are you really going to fight?

35
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,830
Why bother to consider?

36
00:03:48,830 --> 00:03:50,550
Think carefully.

37
00:03:50,550 --> 00:03:52,240
Don’t force me to use my dreadful move.

38
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,390
Dreadful move?

39
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:55,830
I’d like to know

40
00:03:55,830 --> 00:03:56,720
what it is.

41
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,360
Originally,

42
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,550
I was going to

43
00:04:00,550 --> 00:04:01,910
block this cave

44
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:03,630
so you wouldn’t get yourselves killed.

45
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:04,960
But looks like

46
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:07,320
you are still looking for death.

47
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:09,030
I’ll just pull your tongue out

48
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:10,600
to see if you dare to say that again!

49
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:13,440
You just know a formation.

50
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,880
Actually this formation

51
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,440
is easy to be broken.

52
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:19,800
This formation contains

53
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:22,670
the method of the five elements.

54
00:04:22,670 --> 00:04:23,910
One of you beats the gong

55
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:25,440
to trigger the attack from the enemy

56
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,720
and show his weakness,

57
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:29,520
then the other four will come forward.

58
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,440
The five of you guard each other

59
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:33,670
and exchange with other groups.

60
00:04:33,670 --> 00:04:36,440
So the changes will be endless.

61
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:38,470
There are many people who know this.

62
00:04:38,910 --> 00:04:40,080
It’s no big deal!

63
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,550
But few of them

64
00:04:41,550 --> 00:04:42,750
know your weak point, right?

65
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:44,910
Weak point? How could you know?

66
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:47,240
It’s “Jin” on the position “Qian”.

67
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,630
If he is in danger,

68
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:50,320
the other four will also get influenced.

69
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,160
You brat! You told him?

70
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,600
What a cheating jerk!

71
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,350
Why would I tell him that?

72
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:56,880
I’m not with them.

73
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,830
What’s more,

74
00:04:57,830 --> 00:05:00,070
they even made me can’t move.

75
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:01,440
Mr. Yin,

76
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:03,550
it doesn’t matter if you are with us
or not.

77
00:05:03,550 --> 00:05:06,000
But now you have to stand on our side.

78
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,320
Think about it.

79
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,760
If we die,

80
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,230
you have been with Dragon Master
for long

81
00:05:10,230 --> 00:05:11,920
and you know his temper.

82
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,550
Will he let you go?

83
00:05:13,550 --> 00:05:15,480
You will also die with us!

84
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:18,600
Even if you know the way to break
Gong Formation,

85
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,920
will you be strong enough to do that?

86
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,510
Alright,

87
00:05:24,230 --> 00:05:25,270
let’s give it a try then.

88
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:25,850
Back off!

89
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,740
Yes.

90
00:05:49,790 --> 00:05:51,240
I have been waiting for you
the whole night.

91
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:03,510
You’re really bold.

92
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:06,200
Your swordsmanship looks like
from the South,

93
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,880
which is really silly.

94
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:11,350
It doesn’t fit
a beautiful girl like you.

95
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:16,070
I just thought about it.

96
00:06:17,110 --> 00:06:19,480
It’s a pity if you die.

97
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,180
Look.

98
00:06:21,670 --> 00:06:22,960
If you’re willing to follow me,

99
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:24,990
I can forgive

100
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:27,900
everything you have done.

101
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,110
Really?

102
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:32,780
You will have a wealthy life

103
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,680
and servants around you

104
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:37,100
no matter where you are.

105
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:39,880
You can have anything you want.

106
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,990
All the jewelries will belong to you.

107
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:45,340
It’s much better than
how you are living now.

108
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,510
If I kill your people

109
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:49,390
and break your Gong Formation,

110
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:50,760
can you also let this go?

111
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:53,820
Compared with your pretty face,

112
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,540
these are nothing.

113
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:07,200
Tell me what your name is.

114
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:16,510
I like irritable girls.

115
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,510
Look at you guys.

116
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:38,270
You even sent a girl to deal with
Dragon Master.

117
00:07:38,270 --> 00:07:40,790
Don’t you know how despicable he is?

118
00:07:40,790 --> 00:07:42,320
So ignorant!

119
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:55,040
Water Cutting?

120
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:01,740
At this time,

121
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:04,510
that old guy who can’t protect himself

122
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:06,640
still taught you something.

123
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,270
But, unluckily,

124
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:12,200
it won’t work on me.

125
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,670
But it’s already enough to deal with

126
00:08:13,670 --> 00:08:14,640
a loser like you.

127
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:16,030
Wicked girl.

128
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:18,600
You just tricked me with two moves.

129
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,370
I remember

130
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,160
the first time I fought with you,

131
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,760
you were just a green hand who

132
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:29,040
only escaped after playing tricks.

133
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,920
It hasn’t been a few hours

134
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,570
and you have already changed a lot.

135
00:08:34,070 --> 00:08:35,760
Who do you think you are?

136
00:08:36,830 --> 00:08:38,380
I changed my mind.

137
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:41,950
Talents like you

138
00:08:41,950 --> 00:08:44,000
must be killed.

139
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,880
I can’t let you

140
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:47,200
practice for more years.

141
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,480
You have been talking so much.

142
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:51,420
Only this line sounded nice.

143
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:53,200
It won’t cost me

144
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,970
more years to kill you.

145
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,390
How arrogant!

146
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:18,440
Be careful.
He has a close-fitting armor!

147
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,760
No wonder I can’t hurt him.

148
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,760
I thought he was invulnerable.

149
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:27,400
If not for his armor,

150
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:29,030
I would have already

151
00:10:29,030 --> 00:10:30,470
taken his arms off.

152
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,470
What are you doing?

153
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:36,640
Helping you.

154
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,320
About what?

155
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:41,350
Block the blade!

156
00:10:45,110 --> 00:10:46,350
Lad.

157
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:48,080
You have watched enough?

158
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:52,320
There was a craftsman

159
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:54,710
who was said to be able to
perform wonders

160
00:10:54,710 --> 00:10:56,650
and make many great weapons.

161
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,760
Other than that,

162
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,190
there was a Muyun Gauze

163
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,030
which is said to be bright and clear

164
00:11:04,030 --> 00:11:05,150
without flaw.

165
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:06,470
When it’s in the dark,

166
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:08,640
it will be like flowing moonlight.

167
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:09,910
And it’s light.

168
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:11,690
You can be invulnerable wearing it.

169
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:13,690
As far as I know,

170
00:11:14,030 --> 00:11:15,670
the Muyun Gauze

171
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:17,030
was made by Yin Wenlan,
the Mountain Sword,

172
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:18,690
for his wife.

173
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:21,350
Don’t you feel a little bit tight

174
00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:22,720
when wearing it?

175
00:11:24,230 --> 00:11:25,670
What do you want to say?

176
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,860
I’m just curious that

177
00:11:29,230 --> 00:11:31,320
since you got the Yin’s things,

178
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:34,000
why are you not the second
Mountain Sword?

179
00:11:38,470 --> 00:11:39,960
What else do you know?

180
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,840
I know everything.

181
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:45,200
The Color of Ocean and Heaven.

182
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:48,840
Your silver tongue

183
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,110
should be used to buy time,

184
00:11:50,110 --> 00:11:51,670
not to look for death.

185
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:52,990
Dragon Master,

186
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,930
we can talk. Don’t be angry.

187
00:11:56,350 --> 00:11:57,910
Which one of
“The Color of Ocean and Heaven”

188
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:59,400
is your enemy?

189
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,760
You can tell me

190
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,530
and I’ll never say it again.

191
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:06,150
You brat.

192
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:32,440
I knew he is reluctant to kill me.

193
00:12:48,230 --> 00:12:49,040
What are you doing?

194
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,320
Miss Wu,

195
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,520
step aside.

196
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,230
Don’t get hurt.

197
00:13:06,230 --> 00:13:07,150
OK.

198
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,550
Aren’t you already destroyed?

199
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:14,760
You thought the North Blade has been
wiped out

200
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:15,960
so you

201
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:18,300
have been at ease, right?

202
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,470
Zheng Luosheng,

203
00:13:20,470 --> 00:13:23,350
you haven’t made any progress
on your martial arts.

204
00:13:23,350 --> 00:13:25,280
I think I have known the reason.

205
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:28,360
That’s really the North Blade.

206
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,410
You can still stand up again
after being destroyed.

207
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,760
Alright, that’s great.

208
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,550
I have been wanting

209
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:38,770
to see how great the two blades
and one sword are.

210
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:41,330
If I haven’t made

211
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,710
any progress,

212
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,170
I’d like to see how much progress

213
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:48,960
you have made.

214
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,920
I have to ask about one thing first.

215
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:54,520
The Yins are killed by you.

216
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:56,320
You’re not wronged about it, right?

217
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,640
What does it have to do with you?

218
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:02,860
So what if it is or not?

219
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:06,080
Yin Wenlan

220
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:07,580
was a great master.

221
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:12,030
But hundreds of people of his family

222
00:14:12,030 --> 00:14:13,770
died overnight.

223
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:19,360
That has something to do with me.

224
00:14:20,710 --> 00:14:22,220
Since I have got the answer,

225
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,710
it will be easy.

226
00:14:24,710 --> 00:14:25,970
Ji Yunchen,

227
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,650
let alone that you’re disabled.

228
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,970
Even if you are not,

229
00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:34,790
you may not defeat me.

230
00:14:34,790 --> 00:14:36,320
It doesn’t matter

231
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,720
who is stronger

232
00:14:38,470 --> 00:14:40,200
or who is the winner.

233
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:42,590
The point is that today

234
00:14:43,350 --> 00:14:45,060
I’m gonna end your life.

235
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,180
I’d like to see

236
00:14:47,710 --> 00:14:49,670
what trouble a disabled North Blade

237
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:52,550
can make!

238
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:06,840
Mr. Yin,

239
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,150
all you want to see now

240
00:15:08,150 --> 00:15:09,880
must be the death of Dragon Master.

241
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:11,550
Mr. Xie, you’re really smart.

242
00:15:14,590 --> 00:15:16,400
It’s hard to say

243
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:17,960
