244
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:20,520
How about we join hands?

245
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:26,030
His needle…

246
00:15:26,880 --> 00:15:27,950
Let’s talk about it later.

247
00:15:29,710 --> 00:15:30,720
I won’t tell you.

248
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:32,960
Can you put it another way?

249
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,090
Unlock his acupoints first.

250
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,280
Don’t worry.

251
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,400
Since I have agreed to ally,

252
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:39,320
I will keep my words.

253
00:15:58,640 --> 00:15:59,440
I thought

254
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:01,110
being homicidal should be combative.

255
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:02,880
But now

256
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:05,550
I found that being really homicidal

257
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:07,840
is reserved.

258
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,200
Murderous look won’t be visible,

259
00:16:10,030 --> 00:16:11,580
but it’s actually everywhere.

260
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,930
That’s the real killing blade.

261
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,590
The time left for Mr. Ji
is not too much.

262
00:16:16,590 --> 00:16:17,790
After the Soul-searching Needle works,

263
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:18,980
it won’t last long.

264
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,150
I made such a big scene

265
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:57,230
only for you brat.

266
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,990
But now you came yourself.

267
00:17:00,550 --> 00:17:01,670
Pei!

268
00:17:10,230 --> 00:17:13,200
Muyun Gauze really doesn’t fit you.

269
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:20,320
Wicked girl!

270
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:23,790
Miss Zhou!

271
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:45,020
Mr. Ji.

272
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:56,190
“Possessed by wandering soul

273
00:17:56,190 --> 00:17:57,470
and become a wild ghost”.

274
00:17:58,590 --> 00:17:59,400
Soul-searching Needle

275
00:18:00,310 --> 00:18:01,420
