276
00:18:05,230 --> 00:18:06,670
It’s a mystique from far away.

277
00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:09,160
It can make people find back

278
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,270
the vitality.

279
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:13,590
It can cover any illness

280
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,760
or injury you have

