00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,620
Miss Zhou,

286
00:18:32,710 --> 00:18:34,710
before I die,

287
00:18:35,710 --> 00:18:37,580
I could have a fight with you

288
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,850
and teach you the Water Cutting.

289
00:18:43,350 --> 00:18:44,930
It already made me satisfied.

290
00:18:50,520 --> 00:18:54,560
I don’t care about North or South Blade.

291
00:18:54,560 --> 00:18:55,320
I remember

292
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:59,050
Mr. Yin once told me…

293
00:19:00,230 --> 00:19:02,110
In the future,

294
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:04,900
you’ll have many difficulties to face.

295
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:07,310
I just don’t want

296
00:19:07,310 --> 00:19:09,160
you younger generation

297
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,350
to be destroyed in my hand.

298
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,560
Mr. Ji.

299
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:24,950
Pei,

300
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:28,440
I’m sorry.

301
00:19:31,110 --> 00:19:32,360
This is all

302
00:19:34,470 --> 00:19:35,720
I can repay you.

303
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,280
Just go.

304
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:50,700
Do we really have no way to help him?

305
00:20:06,780 --> 00:20:07,730
“Heaven.”

306
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:10,760
“I have always been wanting”

307
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:12,950
“to know you and cherish you.”

308
00:20:12,950 --> 00:20:14,680
“Only when the world comes to an end”

309
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,680
“can I throw away my love for you.”

310
00:20:18,430 --> 00:20:19,680
These scholars

311
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:23,000
always like to show off literary skills.

312
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:24,590
Not like me,

313
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:26,000
who just want to start my own sect

314
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:28,640
after battling with all the masters.

315
00:20:33,190 --> 00:20:35,530
The first place in the world,

316
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:39,070
or the good fame for half a life.

317
00:20:40,350 --> 00:20:41,900
Let all these things

318
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:48,800
go with the wind...

319
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,120
Mr. Yin.

320
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:35,500
You killed Dragon Master,

321
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:37,470
and Mr. Ji is also dead.

322
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:39,250
You have got your revenge.

323
00:21:39,710 --> 00:21:41,190
How about his graciousness to you

324
00:21:41,830 --> 00:21:42,890
for more than ten years?

325
00:21:43,560 --> 00:21:44,780
He has already died.

326
00:21:46,070 --> 00:21:47,120
It’s just what he wanted.

327
00:21:53,760 --> 00:21:55,080
Are you also looking for
the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

328
00:21:58,190 --> 00:21:59,890
It’s none of your business

329
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:01,730
about what I’m going to do.

330
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,420
This belonged to my family.

331
00:22:07,310 --> 00:22:08,810
But Dragon Master once owned it.

332
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,470
So I won’t need it.

333
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,680
It’ll be yours.

334
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,200
If you don’t like it,

335
00:22:15,950 --> 00:22:17,190
you can just throw it.

336
00:22:17,190 --> 00:22:17,710
Mr. Yin!

337
00:22:17,710 --> 00:22:18,610
Chuchu,

338
00:22:19,430 --> 00:22:20,550
just keep it.

339
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:23,830
It will be a dangerous journey.

340
00:22:23,830 --> 00:22:25,190
And you don’t know any martial art.

341
00:22:25,190 --> 00:22:27,640
It can save your life.

342
00:22:28,280 --> 00:22:29,400
Keep it.

343
00:22:44,100 --> 00:22:46,310
<i>Grave of Ji Yunchen</i>

344
00:22:46,310 --> 00:22:49,040
<i>Grave of Ji Yunchen</i>
A great master like Mr. Ji

345
00:22:49,040 --> 00:22:50,560
<i>Grave of Ji Yunchen</i>
could only hide his identity

346
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:52,470
<i>Grave of Ji Yunchen</i>
and be known by no other people.

347
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:54,230
<i>Grave of Ji Yunchen</i>
He shocked the world

348
00:22:54,230 --> 00:22:55,880
when first showed up.

349
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:59,070
Today I’m lucky to see the Water Cutting
come back to the world.

350
00:22:59,070 --> 00:23:01,190
I’ll always remember it.

351
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:02,830
Mr. Ji said

352
00:23:02,830 --> 00:23:04,070
the Blade should be used to do things,

353
00:23:04,070 --> 00:23:05,350
not to bring someone fame.

354
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:08,430
Here, I promise you that

355
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,590
the Water Cutting won’t be lost.

356
00:23:10,590 --> 00:23:13,710
I’ll live up to the blade in my hand.

357
00:23:14,710 --> 00:23:17,350
Back then, he was heroic and free.

358
00:23:17,350 --> 00:23:20,520
<i>Grave of Ji Yunchen</i>
But now, he is buried in a small tomb.

359
00:23:21,470 --> 00:23:22,520
Mr. Ji spent all his life

360
00:23:22,520 --> 00:23:24,160
to make up for this mistake.

361
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:25,430
No matter how,

362
00:23:25,430 --> 00:23:27,230
that’s all written off now.

363
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:29,110
I really admire

364
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:31,160
your broad mind.

365
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,880
Hope in the next life

366
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:35,310
you can achieve all your ambitions

367
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:36,880
and goals.

368
00:23:37,190 --> 00:23:39,040
Mr. Ji,

369
00:23:39,040 --> 00:23:40,110
we all know

370
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:42,090
the one you cared the most is Yin Pei.

371
00:23:43,190 --> 00:23:44,830
Hope he can understand

372
00:23:44,830 --> 00:23:46,880
your good intention as soon as possible

373
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:48,760
and come back to the right way,

374
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:51,000
living up to the Yins’
chivalrous quality.

375
00:24:39,560 --> 00:24:41,070
Li Sheng,

376
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:44,040
I’m curious about something.

377
00:24:44,040 --> 00:24:46,110
Why don’t you learn the
Snow-breaking Blade

378
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:47,980
from your grandpa and father,

379
00:24:48,520 --> 00:24:50,470
but use Double Blades?

380
00:24:51,470 --> 00:24:53,040
Many schools are mixed together

381
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:55,430
in the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

382
00:24:56,430 --> 00:24:57,560
When I was little,

383
00:24:57,950 --> 00:24:59,100
I liked to run around

384
00:24:59,470 --> 00:25:01,230
and liked everything I saw.

385
00:25:01,230 --> 00:25:03,230
Then I learned what I liked.

386
00:25:03,230 --> 00:25:04,950
Back then, I thought Double Blades

387
00:25:04,950 --> 00:25:07,560
might be stronger than a single blade
or sword.

388
00:25:07,950 --> 00:25:09,640
So I learned

389
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:11,620
the Double Blades from Xiaoxiang Sect.

390
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:14,350
Later I wanted to learn the South Blade.

391
00:25:14,350 --> 00:25:15,310
But I didn’t

392
00:25:15,310 --> 00:25:17,370
know how to tell my aunt.

393
00:25:18,510 --> 00:25:20,340
That’s why my swordsmanship

394
00:25:20,520 --> 00:25:21,800
is not that great now.

395
00:25:24,310 --> 00:25:27,140
It’s rare for you to be introspective.

396
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:28,550
Actually,

397
00:25:29,280 --> 00:25:32,160
it doesn’t matter whether it’s from

398
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:34,350
your ancestors or other sects.

399
00:25:34,350 --> 00:25:36,310
You’re Li Zheng’s grandson.

400
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:38,920
But you don’t have to learn
the South Blade.

401
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:40,710
If you’re the son of a fisherman,

402
00:25:40,710 --> 00:25:43,830
you don’t have to learn fishing.

403
00:25:43,830 --> 00:25:46,350
You should ask yourself

404
00:25:46,350 --> 00:25:48,590
about the truth inside this.

405
00:25:49,760 --> 00:25:52,000
I found that your swordsmanship

406
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:55,210
is kind of complicated and limited.

407
00:25:55,950 --> 00:25:58,760
That’s because you have too many
distracting thoughts.

408
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:00,880
Especially while learning Double Blades,

409
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:04,320
you have to be more concentrated.

410
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:07,120
Hope you can

411
00:26:07,830 --> 00:26:10,470
gradually learn the swordsmanship

412
00:26:10,470 --> 00:26:12,760
I taught you these days.

413
00:26:12,950 --> 00:26:15,400
You did teach me some formations.

414
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:17,430
When did you teach me swordsmanship?

415
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:21,800
Everything in the world
is of the same method.

416
00:26:21,800 --> 00:26:25,190
Generally speaking, the formation
is the swordsmanship,

417
00:26:25,190 --> 00:26:27,430
and the swordsmanship is the formation.

418
00:26:27,430 --> 00:26:29,450
It depends on how you understand it.

419
00:26:31,470 --> 00:26:33,380
I’m leaving now.

420
00:26:33,710 --> 00:26:34,970
Take care.

421
00:26:36,470 --> 00:26:37,470
Sir,

422
00:26:37,470 --> 00:26:39,350
let me stay with you for some more days.

423
00:26:39,350 --> 00:26:41,430
Don’t bother.

424
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,800
Then where are you going

425
00:26:43,800 --> 00:26:45,070
next?

426
00:26:47,430 --> 00:26:49,640
I’ll go travel around.

427
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,800
Since Qi School is gone,

428
00:26:52,590 --> 00:26:54,490
I’ll be cosmopolitan.

429
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:19,640
We have been walking for hours.

430
00:27:20,070 --> 00:27:22,520
It’s hard for Chuchu to come

431
00:27:22,520 --> 00:27:23,680
such a long way with us.

432
00:27:24,950 --> 00:27:26,000
Actually,

433
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:27,800
it’s even harder for you.

434
00:27:27,800 --> 00:27:28,920
After fighting with Dragon Master,

435
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:30,430
you can still walk such a long way.

436
00:27:30,430 --> 00:27:31,450
You are strong.

437
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:34,570
Are you praising me or insulting me?

438
00:27:35,110 --> 00:27:36,710
Praising, of course.

439
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,640
Looks like I have to practice more

440
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:42,350
on how to praise others.

441
00:27:42,350 --> 00:27:43,800
It depends on if Miss Zhou

442
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:45,680
will give me the chance.

443
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:47,950
Yeah.

444
00:27:47,950 --> 00:27:49,640
I should give you an attack.

445
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,080
That’s too hard.

446
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:53,230
Fei…

447
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,880
There is a deserted house.

448
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,280
Let’s go have a rest there.

449
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:00,950
OK. I will go first

450
00:28:00,950 --> 00:28:02,210
to clean up the deserted inn.

451
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:08,630
Fei,

452
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,000
sorry.

453
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:11,490
Why?

454
00:28:12,430 --> 00:28:14,640
You and Xie are martial artists.

455
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:15,560
I walked so slow

456
00:28:15,560 --> 00:28:17,230
and held you back.

457
00:28:17,230 --> 00:28:19,160
That’s not like that.
Don’t think too much.

458
00:28:44,470 --> 00:28:46,950
Fei, what’s wrong?

459
00:28:46,950 --> 00:28:49,400
It’s OK. I have suppressed it.

460
00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:52,360
The Yellow and Green Spirit
caused trouble again?

461
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,690
Let me tell Xie.

462
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,280
No. Don’t.

463
00:28:55,280 --> 00:28:56,430
It’s OK now.

464
00:28:56,430 --> 00:28:57,720
Don’t let him worry.

465
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,510
Ladies, welcome.

466
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:18,640
Good job.

467
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:19,800
Here, have a seat.

468
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:21,190
Master, have a seat.

469
00:29:21,190 --> 00:29:22,560
Move it backward a little bit.

470
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:23,190
OK.

471
00:29:30,760 --> 00:29:31,830
Fei,

472
00:29:31,830 --> 00:29:33,470
if we meet a rival like Dragon Master
again,

473
00:29:33,470 --> 00:29:35,160
don’t act rashly.

474
00:29:35,560 --> 00:29:37,230
Then, should I be a coward like you?

475
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,630
Turns out that I’m always a coward
in your mind.

476
00:29:43,430 --> 00:29:43,880
I…

477
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,230
Fei!

478
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:18,780
“The old stones along the bridge
were covered with frost.”

479
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:24,010
“A man who travels far from home
will never return.”

480
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,560
It’s your new work?

481
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:30,800
New poem.

482
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,040
“Coward’s Forlornness”.

483
00:30:34,520 --> 00:30:35,860
It was a bad joke.

484
00:30:36,830 --> 00:30:37,870
You’re not a coward.

485
00:30:39,430 --> 00:30:40,280
Fei,

486
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:42,590
you knew you couldn’t beat
Dragon Master.

487
00:30:42,590 --> 00:30:45,000
Why did you promise Mr. Ji to do that?

488
00:30:47,830 --> 00:30:48,910
I just wonder

489
00:30:49,760 --> 00:30:52,110
why they could be so confidently

490
00:30:52,110 --> 00:30:53,620
and proudly evil.

491
00:30:54,110 --> 00:30:55,640
How can these villains

492
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:56,590
be so proud of

493
00:30:56,590 --> 00:30:57,520
the gross injustice they did

494
00:30:57,520 --> 00:30:59,400
more than 20 years ago

495
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:01,110
while the good guys

496
00:31:01,110 --> 00:31:02,970
were already buried in earth?

497
00:31:03,470 --> 00:31:04,470
They are just spoiled

498
00:31:04,470 --> 00:31:06,150
by the silence of many people.

499
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:15,600
My new poem

500
00:31:16,040 --> 00:31:17,870
is a story about a deserter.

501
00:31:19,110 --> 00:31:20,680
What’s interesting about a deserter?

502
00:31:21,830 --> 00:31:23,190
What’s interesting about a hero?

503
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:24,310
For the leisure time,

504
00:31:24,310 --> 00:31:26,190
why don’t we have some stories
about being a coward?

505
00:31:27,560 --> 00:31:29,160
Alright, alright.

506
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,070
If there is a chance,

507
00:31:30,070 --> 00:31:31,830
I will tell the whole world

508
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:33,400
with eagerness and zest

509
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:35,350
that you, Xie Yun, are not a coward.

510
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:37,420
Thank you then.

511
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:43,110
You can go on

512
00:31:43,110 --> 00:31:44,520
with your story about the deserter.

513
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:46,680
I really want to listen to it.

514
00:31:51,070 --> 00:31:53,230
Before he became a deserter,

515
00:31:53,230 --> 00:31:55,690
he thought he was a great hero

516
00:31:56,590 --> 00:31:58,230
who could return home in honor

517
00:31:58,230 --> 00:32:00,500
and marry the girl he loved.

518
00:32:02,040 --> 00:32:03,640
But later he found

519
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:05,430
that the government

520
00:32:05,430 --> 00:32:06,800
didn’t need him at all

521
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:09,510
and even didn’t regard him as a human.

522
00:32:11,430 --> 00:32:13,730
He was just a living bait
to lure the enemy.

523
00:32:14,110 --> 00:32:15,560
His mission would be completed

524
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:16,860
the moment when he died.

525
00:32:18,350 --> 00:32:19,180
So,

526
00:32:20,110 --> 00:32:21,020
he fled away.

527
00:33:28,560 --> 00:33:29,830
Anzhi,

528
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:31,350
with all my life’s work,

529
00:33:31,350 --> 00:33:32,830
I temporarily shut

530
00:33:32,830 --> 00:33:34,880
-the poison in your veins.
-Uncle!

531
00:33:36,110 --> 00:33:38,800
After that, you can no longer
use martial arts,

532
00:33:38,800 --> 00:33:41,680
but, live well on behalf of me.

533
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:50,590
And then? What are you thinking about?

534
00:33:50,590 --> 00:33:52,190
What happened to that deserter?

535
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:53,770
Nothing.

536
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:56,920
But when the deserter returned home

537
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:57,830
after many difficulties,

538
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,360
he didn’t find his girl.

539
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:00,900
Why?

540
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:05,000
Because that girl is a…

541
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:05,950
Weed Spirit.

542
00:34:05,950 --> 00:34:07,480
She had left riding a carp.

543
00:34:11,160 --> 00:34:12,590
I… I have had enough rest.

544
00:34:13,160 --> 00:34:14,560
I’ll go find some food there.

545
00:34:28,830 --> 00:34:29,920
Fei!

546
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:31,280
Fei!

547
00:34:38,040 --> 00:34:39,680
Oh, no. Her pulse condition is bad.

548
00:34:39,680 --> 00:34:41,230
It must be because of the two spirits.

549
00:34:41,230 --> 00:34:42,760
What to do now?

550
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:43,430
Hengyang.

551
00:34:43,430 --> 00:34:45,230
Someone in Hengyang can save her.

552
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:45,830
But…

553
00:34:45,830 --> 00:34:47,760
But what? Go ahead.

554
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:48,920
She is on the move.

555
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,680
I’m not sure if she is in the city.

556
00:34:50,680 --> 00:34:52,200
We have to give it a try.

557
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,610
Who is it?

558
00:35:23,080 --> 00:35:25,230
Fei, if you can hear me,

559
00:35:25,230 --> 00:35:26,630
do me a favor.

560
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:28,690
We should escape now to save you.

561
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:29,790
Your Majesty?

562
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,710
Greeting, Your Majesty.

563
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:32,900
General Feiqing?

564
00:35:35,600 --> 00:35:37,280
You’ve really kept a close following.

565
00:35:38,630 --> 00:35:39,410
